{{lowercase|title=unit++}}

'''unit++''' is a [[Unit_Test|unit testing]] framework module for [[C++]]. The author started it as an alternative to [[CPPunit]], which he felt was insufficiently integrated into the C++ language.

==External links==
*[http://unitpp.sourceforge.net/ Project's site].


